{"tid":2379889,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"插圖屋宣布減產：每日更新轉為不定期更新","createTime":"2021-01-25T13:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T00:25:27.000Z","uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c4daec4ec120ce50bc5da882d3efacc2481ea6","tid":2379889,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/kaisya_tousan_fuwatari.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fkaisya_tousan_fuwatari.png&h=666ccabc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E8%90%AC%E8%83%BD%E5%9C%96%E5%BA%AB%E3%80%8C%E6%8F%92%E5%9C%96%E5%B1%8B%E3%80%8D%E6%B8%9B%E7%94%A3-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%25BA%25AB%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%258F%2592%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%25B1%258B%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25B8%259B%25E7%2594%25A3-1024x576.jpg&h=cd9ee6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1月25日最新宣布減產：每日更新轉為不定期更新<br />\n<br />\n1月25日，插圖屋的作者(みふね)在網站上發表了名為「有關網站今後的更新」的文章，表示這九年來每天更新和其他接踵而來的事情都令他幾乎沒有休息，因此決定於1月31日起暫停更新網站，在2月好好休息後，再開始不定期的更新。作者希望可以「在不勉強自己的範圍內在各種事情上努力」，又表示大家可以繼續使用素材。假如肺炎令社會需要用上插圖，他會作出對應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.irasutoya.com/2021/01/blog-post_764.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irasutoya.com%2F2021%2F01%2Fblog-post_764.html&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABc0BU04RHr%2BP31d0xuhNw0M%3D&h=3d67ab4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.irasutoya.com/2021/01/blog-post_764.html</a>"},{"pid":"a3c1b50b0866a3b1484e1a85cdc2a1f373b7f6e2","tid":2379889,"uid":154284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T00:25:27.000Z","msg":"原來佢每日更新咁癲嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早幾